# SkyeGateFS13 — Ultimate Environment Template
# Canonical repo-wide deployment and integration sheet for the sovereign gate.
# Fill this out for Netlify production or `netlify dev`.
#
# Philosophy:
# - SkyeGateFS13 is the parent authority.
# - Platforms can keep local app state, but privileged access should route through the gate.
# - Shared vendor credentials can be gate-owned and metered.
# - Customers can also bring their own credentials through the sovereign vault.
# - This is the only canonical env contract file. Do not split it into duplicate mirrors.

